			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.15.2026::9:12:32</_modifiedTime>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 Add sub-requirements per sensor\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID e15c09c6-f726-4ecd-8bf1-b77b36098998</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Machine_Learning</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.15.2026::14:42:10</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.15.2026::14:42:10</_modifiedTime>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 The system shall apply machine learning algorithms to enhance predictive accuracy of the system by learning from historical data and improving real-time risk assessment.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
			<reqID type="a">REQ_02</reqID>
		</IRequirement>
		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID 4e6bfde6-9e64-4ea7-99cd-9ff73ac13304</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Evaluate_Thresholds</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.15.2026::16:13:29</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.15.2026::16:13:29</_modifiedTime>
			<_lastID type="a">1</_lastID>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 The system shall evaluate predefined thresholds for seismic activity, storm intensity, and water pressure, and generate alerts when thresholds are exceeded.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
			<reqID type="a">REQ_03</reqID>
