			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 Seismic and oceanographic data shall be integrated into predictive models to assess the likelihood, intensity and potential impact of a tsunami.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
