			<_name type="a">Relay_Information_REQ</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:48</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:48</_modifiedTime>
			<_lastID type="a">1</_lastID>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 System output data and information shall be disseminated to relevant stakeholders.\par%0D
This information shall be used to potentially prepare measures against possible threats.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
			<AggregatesList type="e">
				<value>GUID 37e17d49-9941-4c39-a529-bb91853910c6</value>
