		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID 37e17d49-9941-4c39-a529-bb91853910c6</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Notify_Government_REQ</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:27</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:27</_modifiedTime>
			<_lastID type="a">1</_lastID>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 Storm trajectories and predicted impact zones of potential disasters shall be relayed by the system to government agencies in case of potential emergency to coordinate disaster response.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID 3bddfa47-2394-4723-a0f9-f862ea5597c3</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Notify_Public_REQ</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:32</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:32</_modifiedTime>
			<_lastID type="a">1</_lastID>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 Weather updates shall be relayed by the system to civilians for their specific region.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID f67987ea-ce96-4b73-a616-ccc09522eba2</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Notify_Researchers_REQ</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:37</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:37</_modifiedTime>
			<_lastID type="a">1</_lastID>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 The system shall make sensor data available in a format accessible to external research institutions for long-term meteorological and oceanographic analysis.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID 27bd2e5d-e433-4304-bf60-4afb81758a5b</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Notify_EmergencyResponders_REQ</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:41</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.16.2026::11:18:41</_modifiedTime>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 Storm trajectories and predicted impact zones of imminent disasters shall be relayed by the system to emergency responders and meteorologists.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
		<IRequirement type="e">
			<_id type="a">GUID 12949088-8949-4ca0-bd4d-115dfda809c3</_id>
			<_myState type="a">8192</_myState>
			<_name type="a">Send_Alerts_REQ</_name>
			<_modifiedTimeWeak type="a">5.16.2026::11:19:14</_modifiedTimeWeak>
			<_modifiedTime type="a">5.16.2026::11:19:14</_modifiedTime>
			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 Actionable information shall be sent through multiple channels to relevant areas in case of imminent danger.\par%0D
This include severity, expected impact, and recommended actions.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
