			<_body type="a">{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1043{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}}%0D
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\fs20 In case of emergency, news outlets shall be used to relay an alert to the affected region.\par%0D
}%0D
</_body>
		</IRequirement>
